data.description: Motivated Seller offers 5K towards Rate Buy Down or Closing Costs on top of a 40K price drop! Bring your offers for this meticulously maintained home with a beautiful kitchen, granite countertops, large island, modern appliances and great floorplan that opens seamlessly to the dining and living areas. The primary suite offers a private retreat with its wall of windows, walk-in closet, an en-suite bathroom with double vanities, a soaking tub and separate shower. Two additional bedrooms near the front provide flexibility for a growing family, guests, or a home office. PLUS, this home was selected by HGTV for an upcoming House Hunters show! Located in Sandbrock Ranch, a master planned community inspired by a natural connection to the land, is only 6 miles from the new PGA headquarters and DNT. Amenities include a carriage house, resort style pool and splash pad, fitness center, stocked fishing lakes, community patio and fire pit area, treehouse, dog park and a new elementary school.
